<br>
Your problems are your own.  Just as my problems are my own.  If a melee doesn't roll on a parchement it should be their choice and not one foisted on to them by people who think they some how have a greater right to something everyone worked equally to obtain.<br>
<br>
This of course doesn't apply to friends or guild groups.<br>
